result.execSummary:
The defendant Michael C. Bryant was found guilty of the following charge(s) in this case. One or more other charges in this case were dismissed. The dismissed charges were not proven and have no legal effect. Michael C. Bryant is presumed innocent of the dismissed charges.

  • Michael C. Bryant was found guilty of Possession of THC (2nd+ Offense), a class I felony, Wisconsin Statutes 961.41(3g)(e).
